<tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><img border="0" src="../triangle.JPG"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="#004242"><b>PERMAFROST GOBLINS</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Group / Solo:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Group</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Mob Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">14 to 22</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Permafrost</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Location:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">+400 +300</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Character Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">16 to 26</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Strategy:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Ok, this is pretty simple hunting and great XP.  It is even better with the experience patch.  Anyway, onto the hunting!
<br><br>
Ok, well what I did is got a friend and headed to Permafrost thinking that we were going to be slaughtered.  But hey, why not try something other than big mammoths ;)
<br><br>
Once we got there we were automatically faced by a Ice Goblin and were attacked.  I took hits while he summoned his pet.  Then he sent pet in and I summoned pet.  I cast one DD spell, and so did he.  The mob fell very quickly, and was great XP.  We started to med up near the zone line.  After medding to full we got up and were faced by 3 mobs.  I shielded my pet and he did the same to his.  I cast my DD spell on the highest mob and all 3 came running as we sent our pets.  We both cast a DD on each creature and they fell quickly.  We still had half our mana.  So we healed up our pets and I pulled from around the corner.  As you go deeper into Permafrost, you find the same mob for a long time.  Also, the same mob will turn to even and even to gamble.  I ventured very far and reached a red, but decided to turn back.  The spawn time is about 5 minutes.
<br><br>
Thank you for listening and good luck!!  Once I reach 20 with my buddy Yassaby I will venture even farther and inform everyone.  Good hunting to you all!!
<br><br>
Wassabee<br>
Druzzil Ro<br>
